item.title: TME
item.description: score:166 Chances: Tencent Music Entertainment Group has renewed a multi-year strategic licensing agreement with Universal Music Group, demonstrating a strong commitment to creating value for artists and exceptional experiences for music lovers. The company’s stock may see a positive impact as music streaming stocks are anticipated to rise steadily in the future, with many of them having great future prospects.
